WEBVTT

00:00.069 --> 00:01.436
Previously on <i>Suits:</i>

00:01.532 --> 00:03.432
We're suing you and your
entire firm for fraud.

00:03.953 --> 00:06.520
I'm looking at a document that
implicates you in a cover-up.

00:06.522 --> 00:09.257
I savaged his reputation all
because you looked me in the eye

00:09.259 --> 00:11.492
and told me that your hood
was rock solid.

00:11.494 --> 00:13.995
You make it right
on your own or I will.

00:13.997 --> 00:16.163
When were you planning
on telling me this?

00:16.165 --> 00:17.999
Did you find what
you're not looking for?

00:18.001 --> 00:19.033
No, did u find
what you're not looking for?

00:19.035 --> 00:20.201
Nope.

00:20.203 --> 00:21.435
That document never
came into this office.

00:21.437 --> 00:22.637
Where the hell is Donna?

00:22.639 --> 00:24.038
She's in the file room.

00:24.040 --> 00:25.239
Hasn't found
that document yet.

00:25.241 --> 00:27.041
Anyone could have
seen it and missed it.

00:27.043 --> 00:28.776
I need to know
that didn't happen,

00:28.778 --> 00:32.012
or I need to know
who to fire.

